name: A Phase or Not a Phase (Jakarta - Matsuyama: Poems #4 of 10)
description:
This is the 4th poem in the collection of poems 'Jakarta-Matsuyama: Poems'.

There was a time when most urban teenagers felt related to the songs of My Chemical Romance. As they grew older, the anger in MCR's songs turned into something somewhat ironic.
